<div id="review_189221083" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/189221083" />
    <a title="Jerrie Ott" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5433304-jerrie-ott"><img alt="Jerrie Ott" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1309528768p2/5433304.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/189221083?book_show_action=true">Jul 25, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jerrie Ott" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jerrie Ott" href="/user/show/5433304-jerrie-ott">Jerrie Ott</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/10364430-the-seville-communion">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer189221083" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13339538278125824468">The characters were very vivid and well developed, but the pace was incredibly slow for my taste. I found the story line compelling, but I never really got into the book. I still have high hopes for Perez-Reverte&apos;s other novels.</span>
  <span id="freeText13339538278125824468" style="display:none">The characters were very vivid and well developed, but the pace was incredibly slow for my taste. I found the story line compelling, but I never really got into the book. I still have high hopes for Perez-Reverte's other novels.</span>
