<span id="freeTextContainer5037145484549654720">When someone has hacked into the Pope&apos;s personal computer and left a message about a church killing to protect itself, Father Lorenzo Quart of the Institute for External Affairs which coordinates the secret activities of the Vatican&apos;s Information Services. The IEA is also referred to as God&apos;s Left Hand or the Dirty Works Department. Father Quart is sent to Seville, Spain to investigate and to try to find out who the hacker is. Very interesting politics. Well written.</span>
  <span id="freeText5037145484549654720" style="display:none">When someone has hacked into the Pope's personal computer and left a message about a church killing to protect itself, Father Lorenzo Quart of the Institute for External Affairs which coordinates the secret activities of the Vatican's Information Services. The IEA is also referred to as God's Left Hand or the Dirty Works Department. Father Quart is sent to Seville, Spain to investigate and to try to find out who the hacker is. Very interesting politics. Well written.</span>
